text: Skilled in Java, Spring Boot, MySQL, REST APIs, and Microservices. Worked on backend development for ecommerce platform.
Developed banking application using Python, Flask, SQLite and JWT Authentication. Good understanding of OOP and Git.
Experience with C#, .NET Core, SQL Server, LINQ, and Azure cloud deployment. Built desktop inventory management app.
Worked on Android development using Kotlin, Firebase, MVVM, and Retrofit. Published app on Play Store.
Built scalable backend services using Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and Redis with JWT auth.
Designed responsive websites using HTML, CSS, JavaScript and Tailwind CSS. Familiar with SEO and UI/UX.
Experience in React.js, Redux, REST APIs, Firebase and building dashboards. Worked on portfolio website.
Built WordPress websites with custom themes and plugins. Experienced in PHP and MySQL.
Familiar with MERN stack: MongoDB, Express, React, Node. Built social media clone project.
Skilled in Bootstrap, jQuery, AJAX and integrating third-party APIs. Built real estate listing website.
Skilled in Excel, SQL, Power BI, and data cleaning. Created dashboards for sales and revenue analysis.
Worked on ETL pipelines, Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, and Seaborn. Built data visualization for healthcare dataset.
Experience in Tableau, MySQL, forecasting models, and KPI reporting for marketing data.

Built Excel-based MIS reports, automated analytics with Python, and worked with CSV and SQL datasets.
